            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Thanks Justin,\r\nThe idea was to get a hook that will allow triggering certain actions related to the presence of these markers (e.g., after performing a git pull). It can be implemented within a BufRead but that is not efficient for large files. Git being a universal requirements for programming these days, I thought it would make sense to have this hook natively (almost like what neovim does now with FileType; which is another way of implementing this).",
